These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, spy, drama, romance, western, mystery, crime
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: electronic, pop, country, ambient, house, funk, d&b
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: weightlifting, cycling, swimming, basketball, sailing, baseball, biathlon
 1. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the fan of pop and the fan of electronic##2
 4. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 5. the fan of pop is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 6. the person watching action movies is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 7. the fan of ambient is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person watching western movies##2
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
10. the person watching crime movies is the fan of country##1
11. the fan of funk is the person watching romance movies##1
12. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
13. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the fan of house##1
14. the person watching mystery movies is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is biathlon##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | western | action     | mystery | spy | romance | crime  | drama  |
| Music-Genre   | electronic  | ambient        | pop  | d&b     | funk   | country       | house   |
| Sport         | cycling   | biathlon | basketball    | swimming  | sailing | baseball | weightlifting |

