.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: pakistani, australian, russian, turkish, indonesian, dutch, chinese
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: volleyball, skateboarding, surfing, tennis, rugby, basketball, rowing
The people use 7 different means of transport: snowmobile, motorbike, boat, taxi, subway, bike, tram
 1. the australian is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is the chinese##1
 6. the pakistani is the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the pakistani is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person driving the tram##2
 8. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the indonesian##1
 9. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
10. the russian is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
11. the indonesian is on the right of the pakistani##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is the australian##1
13. the turkish is on the left of the pakistani##1
14. the turkish is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
15. the australian is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Nationality   | dutch | chinese      | turkish     | pakistani  | indonesian | russian | australian |
| Sport         | skateboarding  | volleyball | basketball | surfing | rowing | tennis   | rugby  |
| Transport     | boat   | bike     | tram        | taxi  | subway   | motorbike       | snowmobile      |

