.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, cola, juice, lemonade, mirinda, hot-chocolate
The people have 7 different jobs:  writer, lawyer, electrician, doctor, nurse, librarian, entrepreneur
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, quad-bike, airplane, jet-ski, bus, subway, skateboard
 1. the person driving the quad-bike is the writer##1
 2. the person driving the bus is the doctor##1
 3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the nurse##1
 4. the person driving the airplane is the person drinking sprite##1
 5. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the skateboard and the entrepreneur##2
 6. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 7. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
 9. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1
10. the electrician is on the right of the librarian##1
11. the person driving the quad-bike is the writer##1
12. the electrician is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
13. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the doctor##1
14. the person driving the skateboard is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
15. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage    | 7up     | lemonade   | mirinda        | sprite   | cola     | juice     | hot-chocolate    |
