.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-4::.
There 7 different types of food: apple, watermelon, cucumber, peas, grapes, mango, corn
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: time-travel, crime, family, martial-arts, epic, mystery, satire
There are 7 different nationalities: german, australian, brazilian, argentine, pakistani, russian, indonesian
 1. the pakistani is on the far left##1
 2. the person watching mystery movies is the person eating peas##1
 3. the brazilian is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 4. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
 5. the german is on the right of the person eating mango##1
 6. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating apple is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 9. the russian is the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the german is the person eating grapes##1
11. the person watching family movies is the indonesian##1
12. the person eating watermelon is the pakistani##1
13. the argentine is on the far right##1
14. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching family movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
15. the person eating corn is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3     |    4    |     5      |     6      |     7     |
