 5. the fan of r&b is the videographer##1
 6. the nurse is in the middle##1
 7. the entrepreneur is the fan of hip-hop##1
 8. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 9. the fan of r&b is the owner of the dog##1
10. the bartender is the owner of the hamster##1
