 7. the owner of the fish is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 8. the owner of the horse is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the owner of the fish##2
 9. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
10. the person who's hobby is video-games is in the middle##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
12. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
13. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
14. the person who's hobby is singing is between the owner of the rat and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
15. the owner of the rat is the person drinking lemonade##1

